    <title>Activision’s big contribution to AI is Call of Duty: Warzone data</title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="A screenshot of player data on Call of Duty: Warzone’s Caldera map." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/3dMlWlONa9n-IldnyPHJe_-NSxY=/69x0:872x535/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73491793/image31.5.png" /&gt;
